snippet.title: Alexis Arc: Heroes of the Three Kingdoms official Auria path gamelay | AlphaDio Production
snippet.description:
Hi again in my Alexis Arc video!
I've released this game in Itch.io for USD 15, but it's 20% off for the first two weeks due to initial release!
This game has 3-sided story: Auria, Callista, and Deminia, but I've just finished only Auria path so far.
Product Link: https://alphadio-production.itch.io/alexis-arc-heroes-of-the-three-kingdoms

AlphaDio Production, Indonesia
